com.m3rcuriel.controve.components

Interface SimpleAccumulatedSensor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ReZeroable

    public interface SimpleAccumulatedSensor
extends ReZeroable
    An abstract representation of a sensor which reads the derivative and accumulates the value. Example: read dx/dt, accumulate to get x.
